{"title":"大地","authors":["沙蕾"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":10,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙蕾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地纵然满目疮痍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可它不会死去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它至多是休克，终会醒来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它相信自己是永生的精灵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它相信世界有希望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炮弹坑会被填平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相信倒塌的篱笆会被扶起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相信灯塔会在风暴中远眺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相信废墟上会造起新居"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子们的欢笑装饰空白的四壁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相信冰冻的河会有绿波"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荆棘道会变成玫瑰路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相信燕子会归来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"故人会欢叙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，大地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"培育了多少信心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甚至矿物也在地下笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相信自己会象种子探出头来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人在大地上行走"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他感到灵魂也会饥渴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命最怕空虚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是无厌足地求索知识"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让智慧堆成山、漫成海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人不相信存在是悲剧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不相信杜鹃会泣血"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不相信露珠是泪滴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命的基调是喜悦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们悲悯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只是悲悯那些迷失的生灵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们一定会援手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的神奇的手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一定会重新创世，造人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人——大地的同谋者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手携手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让天堂，让神仙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让不死之药——和谐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从云端下降"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}